### [Philemon Chapter 1](../../../bib/kjv/plm001.htm#001.md)

Overview

[Plm 1:1](../../../bib/kjv/plm001.htm#001.md), Paul rejoices to hear of the
faith and love of Philemon, whom he desires to forgive his servant
Onesimus, and lovingly to receive him again.

